Off we go on a oh, lets say a hate raid, get up there and raid leaders says &quot;NO PETS&quot; but, but, its an epic pet! answer--no pets sorry<br>
<br>
I was on a chardok raid with one of the few mages that has the epic and we both summoned pets. the only difference was the epic is slightly larger. Not enough that anyone would notice readily. Again at one point .. you guessed it.. kill the pets!<br>
so what it comes down to is: its a pet and pets are not as wanted on raids as we would like..uber or not.<br>
at the very least they should change the graphic so that there is a very distinct look for the epic pet. Let people know what effort we went to! make it look epic!<br>
